features: 🥧【SIZE AND THERMAL INSULATION】 Our lunch bag measures 11.5" x 7" x 8.5" and is designed to keep your food at the desired temperature. It offers excellent thermal insulation, keeping your meals hot or cold for an extended period. Whether you're heading to work or a picnic, this lunch bag ensures your food stays fresh and delicious.

🥧【THREE-LAYER MATERIAL CONSTRUCTION】The lunch bag is made from three layers of high-quality materials. The outer layer is constructed with durable fabric, providing a stylish and easy-to-clean surface. The middle layer features pearl cotton insulation, effectively retaining the temperature inside. The inner layer consists of food-grade aluminum foil, ensuring food safety and maintaining the desired temperature.

🥧【STURDY HANDLE AND MULTIPLE COMPARTMENTS】 The lunch box is equipped with a sturdy handle, allowing for easy and comfortable transportation. It also features a spacious main compartment to accommodate your meals, beverages, snacks, and other essential items. Additionally, there is a front zipper pocket for convenient storage of small personal belongings.

🥧【VERSATILITY FOR VARIOUS ACTIVITIES】Our lunch bag is incredibly versatile and suitable for a wide range of activities. Whether you're going on a trip, enjoying a picnic, camping, or engaging in outdoor activities, this bag is the perfect companion. It provides a convenient and secure way to carry your food and essentials.This lunch bag is suitable for women & men.

🥧【DURABLE AND SAFE DESIGN】The lunch bag is built to last with its sturdy construction and high-quality materials. It is designed to withstand daily use and maintain its functionality. The use of high materials guarantees the safety of your food. Enjoy peace of mind knowing your food is well-protected and easily accessible with our durable and safe lunch bag.
